\sqrt{2\pi n}\left(\frac{n}e\right)^n
\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{n!}{\sqrt{2\pi n}\left(\frac{n}e\right)^n}=1\;.
n\to\infty
\frac{\frac{(2n)!}{n!^2}}{\frac{\sqrt{2\pi(2n)}(2n/e)^{2n}}{\left(\sqrt{2\pi n}(n/e)^n\right)^2}}=\frac{(2n)!}{\sqrt{2\pi(2n)}(2n/e)^{2n}}\cdot\frac{\left(\sqrt{2\pi n}(n/e)^n\right)^2}{n!^2}\to 1^2=1
\binom{2n}n\sim\frac{2^{2n}}{\sqrt{\pi n}}\;.
