\Theta
{2m \choose m}=\frac{(2m)!}{(m!)^2}\sim \frac{\big(\frac{2m}{e}\big)^{2m}\sqrt{4\pi m}}{({\big(\frac{m}{e}\big)^m\sqrt{2\pi m}})^2}
=2^{2m}\frac{\big(\frac{m}{e}\big)^{2m}*2\sqrt{\pi m}}{{\big(\frac{m}{e}\big)^{2m}(2\pi m)}}=\frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{\pi m}}
\color{red}{0.5}\frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{m}} \leq \frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{\pi m}} \leq\color{red}{2}\frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{\pi m}}
{2m\choose m}\sim \frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{\pi m}} = \Theta\big(\frac{2^{2m}}{\sqrt{m}}\big)
